TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT DISTINCT CS_BUSINESSUNIT.NAME AS BU_NAME, AGT.GENERICATTRIBUTE1 AS AGENCY_CODE, 'SGY'||AGT.GENERICATTRIBUTE1 AS AGENCY, AGT.NAME AS POS_NAME, AGT.GENERICATTRIBUTE4 AS COMM_AGT_CLASSCODE, AGT.EFFECTIVESTARTDATE AS EFF_ST, AGT.EFFECTIVEENDDATE AS EFF_END, cs_payee.EFFECTIVESTARTDATE AS PAYEE_EFF_ST, cs_payee.EFFECTIVEENDDATE AS PAYEE_EFF_END, AGY.EFFECTIVESTARTDATE AS AGY_EFF_ST, AGY.EFFECTIVEENDDATE AS AGY_EFF_END, cs_TITLE.NAME as AGY_TITLE, CASE WHEN cs_TITLE.NAME='DISTRICT' OR cs_TITLE.NAME='ORGANISATION' THEN '1' ELSE '0' END AS AGY_IS_DISTRICT_FLAG FROM CS_POSITION AGT INNER JOIN cs_payee ON AGT.REMOVEDATE = TO_DATE ('01/01/2200 00:00:00', 'MM/DD/YYYY HH24:MI:SS') AND cs_payee.removedate = TO_DATE ('01/01/2200 00:00:00', 'MM/DD/YYYY HH24:MI:SS') AND AGT.payeeseq = cs_payee.payeeseq INNER JOIN CS_BUSINESSUNIT ON CS_BUSINESSUNIT.MASK = cs_payee.BUSINESSUNITMAP AND CS_BUSINESSUNIT.PROCESSINGUNITSEQ = AGT.PROCESSINGUNITSEQ INNER JOIN CS_POSITION AGY ON 'SGY'||AGT.GENERICATTRIBUTE1 = AGY.NAME AND AGY.removedate = TO_DATE ('01/01/2200 00:00:00', 'MM/DD/YYYY HH24:MI:SS') INNER JOIN CS_TITLE ON AGY.TITLESEQ = CS_TITLE.RULEELEMENTOWNERSEQ AND CS_TITLE.REMOVEDATE = TO_DATE ('01/01/2200 00:00:00', 'MM/DD/YYYY HH24:MI:SS')

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: POS_NAME = LOOKUP_AGENT AND PAYEE_EFF_ST <= LOOKUP_CONSOLIDATED_DT AND PAYEE_EFF_END > LOOKUP_CONSOLIDATED_DT AND EFF_ST <= LOOKUP_CONSOLIDATED_DT AND EFF_END > LOOKUP_CONSOLIDATED_DT AND AGY_EFF_ST <= LOOKUP_CONSOLIDATED_DT AND AGY_EFF_END > LOOKUP_CONSOLIDATED_DT

TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT DISTINCT agy.NAME AS AGENCY, agy.MANAGERSEQ as AGY_MANAGERSEQ, dis.NAME as DISTRICT, agy.EFFECTIVESTARTDATE AS AGY_EFF_ST, agy.EFFECTIVEENDDATE AS AGY_EFF_END, dis.EFFECTIVESTARTDATE AS DIST_EFF_ST, dis.EFFECTIVEENDDATE AS DIST_EFF_END FROM CS_POSITION agy INNER JOIN CS_POSITION dis on agy.managerseq = dis.ruleelementownerseq where agy.REMOVEDATE = DATE'2200-1-1' and dis.REMOVEDATE = DATE'2200-1-1'

TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT DISTINCT CS_POSITION.NAME as LEADER_CODE, CS_TITLE.NAME AS LEADER_TITLE, CS_POSITION.EFFECTIVESTARTDATE AS EFF_ST, CS_POSITION.EFFECTIVEENDDATE AS EFF_END FROM CS_POSITION, CS_GAPOSITION,CS_TITLE where CS_POSITION.removedate = to_date('01/01/2200 00:00:00', 'MM/DD/YYYY HH24:MI:SS') AND CS_POSITION.RULEELEMENTOWNERSEQ = CS_GAPOSITION.RULEELEMENTOWNERSEQ(+) AND CS_GAPOSITION.removedate(+) = to_date('01/01/2200 00:00:00', 'MM/DD/YYYY HH24:MI:SS') AND CS_GAPOSITION.PAGENUMBER(+) = 0 AND CS_POSITION.effectiveenddate= CS_GAPOSITION.effectiveenddate(+) AND CS_POSITION.TITLESEQ = CS_TITLE.RULEELEMENTOWNERSEQ(+) AND CS_TITLE.removedate(+) =to_date('01/01/2200 00:00:00', 'MM/DD/YYYY HH24:MI:SS') AND CS_POSITION.NAME NOT IN ('Agency Channel','AFA Channel')

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: LEADER_CODE = LOOKUP_LEADER_CODE AND EFF_ST <= LOOKUP_CONSOLIDATED_DT AND EFF_END > LOOKUP_CONSOLIDATED_DT
